{"type":"message","id":"be241cfc","parentId":"3168f964","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:26:51.970Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-09 19:26 EST] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: # TASK: Complete Salesforce Code Auditor Reporting Layer\n\n## CONTEXT\nThe `salesforce-code-auditor` skill has been classified as **PARTIAL** because:\n1. ✅ **Layer 1 (FUNCTIONAL)**: Code analysis works (parsing, dependency extraction)\n2. ❌ **Layer 2 (INCOMPLETE)**: Reporting layer incomplete (templates without filled findings)\n\n## YOUR MISSION\nComplete the reporting layer to make the skill **FULLY FUNCTIONAL**.\n\n## SPECIFIC REQUIREMENTS\n\n### 1. Add Findings Synthesis\nConvert parsed dependencies → specific, actionable findings:\n- **Input**: Parsed dependencies from code analysis\n- **Output**: Specific findings with:\n  - Code location (file:line)\n  - Severity (CRITICAL/HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW)\n  - Pattern detected (SOQL in loop, missing FLS, etc.)\n  - Recommendation (specific fix suggestion)\n  - Impact (performance, security, maintainability)\n\n### 2. Implement Risk Assessment\nCreate risk scoring system:\n- **CRITICAL**: Security vulnerabilities, data loss risks\n- **HIGH**: Performance issues, major design flaws\n- **MEDIUM**: Code quality issues, maintainability concerns\n- **LOW**: Style issues, minor optimizations\n\n### 3. Generate Complete Audit Reports\nProduce reports that:\n- Include executive summary\n- List findings by severity\n- Show code snippets with issues\n- Provide specific recommendations\n- Include dependency graphs\n- Format for architect consumption\n\n### 4. Follow Integration Standards\n- Use formats from `CODE_AUDIT_HANDOFF_MODES.md`\n- Preserve project context\n- Store artifacts in project folder\n- Enable architect to consume findings\n\n## ANTI-SIMULATION RULES\n- NO placeholder findings\n- NO generic recommendations\n- REAL analysis → REAL findings\n- Specific code locations required\n- Actionable recommendations required\n\n## FILES TO CREATE/MODIFY\n1. `scripts/findings_synthesizer.py` - Convert dependencies → findings\n2. `scripts/risk_assessor.py` - Risk scoring system\n3. `scripts/report_generator.py` - Complete report generation\n4. `templates/audit_report_template.md` - Report template\n5. Update existing scripts to use new reporting layer\n\n## DELIVERABLES\n1. **Complete reporting system** with all components\n2. **Test evidence** showing:\n   - Real code → parsed dependencies → specific findings\n   - Risk assessment working\n   - Complete audit reports generated\n   - Reports consumable by architect\n3. **Updated documentation** reflecting complete functionality\n4. **Handoff report** with outcome and evidence\n\n## SUCCESS CRITERIA\n`salesforce-code-auditor` becomes **FUNCTIONAL** when:\n1. Complete reports with specific findings generated\n2. Risk assessment works\n3. Reports are architect-consumable\n4. Evidence shows end-to-end functionality\n\n## TIMELINE\n- Start: Immediate\n- Complete: Within 30 minutes\n- Report: Concise handoff with operational evidence\n\nProceed to complete the reporting layer and make the skill fully functional."}],"timestamp":1773102411968}}
