{"type":"message","id":"f12727ec","parentId":"784fb742","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:27:26.431Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_xJhMaQFsJVlDJpvN2Z5iAIsN","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### Handoff Report\n- **Outcome**: success\n- **Incidents**: none\n- **Files touched**:\n  - skills/salesforce-code-auditor/SKILL.md\n  - skills/salesforce-code-auditor/references/FILE_TYPES.md\n  - skills/salesforce-code-auditor/references/REVIEW_CHECKLISTS.md\n  - skills/salesforce-code-auditor/references/TOKEN_STRATEGY.md\n  - skills/salesforce-code-auditor/references/REPORT_TEMPLATE.md\n  - skills/salesforce-code-auditor/examples/example_intake.md\n  - skills/salesforce-code-auditor/examples/example_manifest.md\n  - skills/salesforce-code-auditor/examples/example_audit_report.md\n  - skills/salesforce-code-auditor/scripts/utils_fs.py\n  - skills/salesforce-code-auditor/scripts/init_case.py\n  - skills/salesforce-code-auditor/scripts/index_inputs.py\n  - skills/salesforce-code-auditor/scripts/detect_entrypoints.py\n  - skills/salesforce-code-auditor/scripts/build_dependency_graph.py\n  - skills/salesforce-code-auditor/scripts/extract_snippets.py\n  - skills/salesforce-code-auditor/scripts/generate_reports.py\n- **Next action**: Use the skill by running init_case.py, index_inputs.py, detect_entrypoints.py, build_dependency_graph.py, generate_reports.py sequentially.\n- **Watchdog fields**:\n  - session_id: agent:main:subagent:7b7243d6-d51b-4b2a-b7b2-0ec5f9389de1\n  - run_id: c7b4bd4c-3a32-4b92-8289-d30c4d450f50\n  - last_activity_at: 2026-03-06T00:30:00Z\n  - progress_marker: skill created, demo executed, reports generated\n\n## Location of generated demo artifacts\n`/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/projects/demo/code_audit/demo_code_audit/`\n\n## Commands to run the skill\n1. Initialize a case:\n   ```bash\n   cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/salesforce-code-auditor/scripts\n   python3 init_case.py --project-key <key> --case-id <case> [--demo]\n   ```\n2. Place source files in the created `inputs/` folder.\n3. Index files:\n   ```bash\n   python3 index_inputs.py --project-key <key> --case-id <case>\n   ```\n4. Detect entrypoints:\n   ```bash\n   python3 detect_entrypoints.py --project-key <key> --case-id <case>\n   ```\n5. Build dependency graph:\n   ```bash\n   python3 build_dependency_graph.py --project-key <key> --case-id <case>\n   ```\n6. Generate reports:\n   ```bash\n   python3 generate_reports.py --project-key <key> --case-id <case> [--emit-incidents]\n   ```\n7. Extract snippets as needed:\n   ```bash\n   python3 extract_snippets.py --project-key <key> --case-id <case> --file <path> --method <method>\n   ```\n\nThe skill is production‑ready, supports token‑efficient progressive analysis, integrates with the learning system, and works together with the `salesforce‑architect` skill."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773102446427}}
