{"type":"message","id":"f0b509e5","parentId":"16040e80","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:36:39.547Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me create the audit report template:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_QN2cKMvDc0KkJqc7UZYeSvHY","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/salesforce-code-auditor/templates/audit_report_template.md","content":"# Salesforce Code Audit Report Template\n\n## Report Metadata\n- **Project Key**: `{{project_key}}`\n- **Audit Case ID**: `{{case_id}}`\n- **Audit Mode**: `{{mode}}` (A=Architecture→Audit, B=Audit→Architecture, C=Design Validation)\n- **Report Date**: `{{report_date}}`\n- **Auditor**: `{{auditor_name}}`\n- **Architect**: `{{architect_name}}`\n\n## Executive Summary\n\n### Overall Assessment\n- **Code Health**: {{code_health}} (POOR/FAIR/GOOD/EXCELLENT)\n- **Overall Risk Level**: {{overall_risk_level}} (CRITICAL/HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW)\n- **Risk Score**: {{overall_risk_score}}/100\n- **Total Findings**: {{total_findings}}\n- **Critical Findings**: {{critical_count}}\n- **High Findings**: {{high_count}}\n\n### Key Takeaways\n1. {{key_takeaway_1}}\n2. {{key_takeaway_2}}\n3. {{key_takeaway_3}}\n\n### Architectural Implications\n{{architectural_implications}}\n\n## Technical Assessment\n\n### Codebase Overview\n- **Files Analyzed**: {{files_analyzed}}\n- **Entry Points**: {{entry_points_count}}\n- **Apex Classes**: {{apex_classes_count}}\n- **Visualforce Pages**: {{vf_pages_count}}\n- **LWC Components**: {{lwc_components_count}}\n- **Triggers**: {{triggers_count}}\n\n### Architecture Patterns Identified\n{{architecture_patterns}}\n\n### Design Quality Assessment\n{{design_quality}}\n\n## Risk Assessment\n\n### Overall Risk Profile\n- **Risk Level**: {{risk_level}}\n- **Risk Score**: {{risk_score}}/100\n- **Primary Risk Categories**:\n  {{risk_categories}}\n\n### Blocking Conditions\n{{blocking_conditions}}\n\n### Risk Mitigation Priority\n1. **Immediate** (Critical): {{immediate_risks}}\n2. **Short-term** (High): {{short_term_risks}}\n3. **Medium-term** (Medium): {{medium_term_risks}}\n4. **Long-term** (Low): {{long_term_risks}}\n\n## Detailed Findings\n\n### CRITICAL Findings (Must Address)\n{{critical_findings}}\n\n### HIGH Findings (Should Address)\n{{high_findings}}\n\n### MEDIUM Findings (Consider Addressing)\n{{medium_findings}}\n\n### LOW Findings (Nice to Have)\n{{low_findings}}\n\n## Recommendations\n\n### Architectural Recommendations\n{{architectural_recommendations}}\n\n### Implementation Recommendations\n{{implementation_recommendations}}\n\n### Security Recommendations\n{{security_recommendations}}\n\n### Performance Recommendations\n{{performance_recommendations}}\n\n### Maintenance Recommendations\n{{maintenance_recommendations}}\n\n## Remediation Plan\n\n### Phase 1: Critical Fixes (Week 1-2)\n{{phase1_remediation}}\n\n### Phase 2: High Priority (Week 3-4)\n{{phase2_remediation}}\n\n### Phase 3: Medium Priority (Month 2)\n{{phase3_remediation}}\n\n### Phase 4: Low Priority (Ongoing)\n{{phase4_remediation}}\n\n## Evidence\n\n### Code Snippets with Issues\n{{code_snippets}}\n\n### Dependency Analysis\n{{dependency_analysis}}\n\n### Performance Metrics\n{{performance_metrics}}\n\n### Security Analysis\n{{security_analysis}}\n\n## Appendices\n\n### Appendix A: Files Analyzed\n{{files_analyzed_list}}\n\n### Appendix B: Dependency Graph\n{{dependency_graph_summary}}\n\n### Appendix C: Execution Trace\n{{execution_trace_summary}}\n\n### Appendix D: Test Matrix\n{{test_matrix_summary}}\n\n## Approval & Sign-off\n\n### Auditor Approval\n- **Name**: _________________________\n- **Role**: Code Auditor\n- **Date**: _________________________\n- **Comments**: _________________________\n\n### Architect Review\n- **Name**: _________________________\n- **Role**: Salesforce Architect\n- **Date**: _________________________\n- **Comments**: _________________________\n\n### Project Manager Acknowledgement\n- **Name**: _________________________\n- **Role**: Project Manager\n- **Date**: _________________________\n- **Comments**: _________________________\n\n---\n\n## Report Generation Details\n- **Tool**: Salesforce Code Auditor Skill\n- **Version**: {{skill_version}}\n- **Generated**: {{generation_timestamp}}\n- **Template Version**: 1.0\n- **Compliance**: Follows CODE_AUDIT_HANDOFF_MODES.md standards"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":89,"output":1036,"cacheRead":42944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44069,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773102964748}}
