{"type":"message","id":"04284c27","parentId":"8f4d9872","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:46:34.378Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_rt6203iMgEVM9ZzaLnnM3KtN","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Risk Assessment Report\n\n## Executive Summary\n- **Overall Risk Level**: HIGH\n- **Overall Risk Score**: 54.33/100\n- **Total Findings**: 3\n- **Critical Findings**: 0\n- **High Findings**: 2\n\n## Risk by Category\n\n### Security\n- **Average Risk Score**: 72.0/100\n- **Finding Count**: 1\n- **Percentage of Total**: 33.3%\n\n### Performance\n- **Average Risk Score**: 56.0/100\n- **Finding Count**: 1\n- **Percentage of Total**: 33.3%\n\n### Data Quality\n- **Average Risk Score**: 35.0/100\n- **Finding Count**: 1\n- **Percentage of Total**: 33.3%\n\n## Blocking Conditions Analysis\n\n### ❌ CRITICAL Blockers (Must be addressed)\n- **FLS_MISSING** in `DemoController.cls:6`\n  - Missing FLS/CRUD checks for DML operation\n\n### ⚠️ HIGH Blockers (Should be addressed)\n- **RECURSION_RISK** in `DemoTrigger.trigger:1`\n  - No recursion guard detected\n\n### 🔍 Requires Architect Review\nThese findings should be reviewed by the architect for impact assessment:\n- **VALIDATION_MISSING** in `DemoTrigger.trigger:1`\n\n## Detailed Risk Assessment\n\n### FLS_MISSING - CRITICAL Risk\n- **Location**: `DemoController.cls:6`\n- **Category**: Security\n- **Risk Score**: 72/100 (Impact: 8/10, Likelihood: 9/10)\n- **Remediation Effort**: Low\n- **Business Impact**: Data access control failure\n- **Description**: Missing FLS/CRUD checks for DML operation\n- **Recommendation**: Add Schema.SObjectType.field.isAccessible() checks\n- **Code Snippet**:\n```\ninsert acc;\n```\n\n### RECURSION_RISK - HIGH Risk\n- **Location**: `DemoTrigger.trigger:1`\n- **Category**: Performance\n- **Risk Score**: 56/100 (Impact: 7/10, Likelihood: 8/10)\n- **Remediation Effort**: Low\n- **Business Impact**: Infinite loops, governor limits\n- **Description**: No recursion guard detected\n- **Recommendation**: Add static Boolean variable to prevent recursion\n- **Code Snippet**:\n```\nTrigger without recursion guard\n```\n\n### VALIDATION_MISSING - MEDIUM Risk\n- **Location**: `DemoTrigger.trigger:1`\n- **Category**: Data Quality\n- **Risk Score**: 35/100 (Impact: 5/10, Likelihood: 7/10)\n- **Remediation Effort**: Low\n- **Business Impact**: Data quality issues\n- **Description**: Before insert trigger without explicit validation\n- **Recommendation**: Add data validation logic\n- **Code Snippet**:\n```\nBefore insert context used\n```\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773103594373}}
